queries.sql: SELECT MONTH(created_at) as bulan, COUNT(*) as jumlah_pesanan, SUM(total_harga) as total_pendapatan, SUM(CASE WHEN status = 'selesai' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as pesanan_selesai, SUM(CASE WHEN status = 'dibatalkan' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as pesanan_dibatalkan FROM `pesanan` WHERE YEAR(created_at) = '2025' GROUP BY MONTH(created_at) ORDER BY MONTH(created_at) ASC

SELECT YEAR(created_at) as tahun, COUNT(*) as total_pesanan, SUM(total_harga) as total_pendapatan, SUM(CASE WHEN status = 'selesai' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as pesanan_selesai, SUM(CASE WHEN status = 'dibatalkan' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as pesanan_dibatalkan, AVG(total_harga) as rata_rata_pesanan FROM `pesanan` WHERE YEAR(created_at) = '2025' GROUP BY YEAR(created_at) ORDER BY YEAR(created_at) DESC

queries.sql: SELECT MONTH(created_at) as bulan, COUNT(*) as jumlah_pesanan, SUM(total_harga) as total_pendapatan, SUM(CASE WHEN status = 'selesai' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as pesanan_selesai, SUM(CASE WHEN status = 'dibatalkan' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as pesanan_dibatalkan FROM `pesanan` WHERE YEAR(created_at) = '2025' GROUP BY MONTH(created_at) ORDER BY MONTH(created_at) ASC

SELECT `p`.`id`, `p`.`kode_pesanan`, `p`.`nama_lengkap`, `p`.`no_whatsapp`, `p`.`email`, `p`.`jenis_layanan`, `p`.`tanggal_acara`, `p`.`tanggal_acara` as `event_date`, `p`.`lokasi_acara`, `p`.`status`, `p`.`total_harga`, `p`.`dp_dibayar`, `p`.`catatan_admin`, `pm`.`nama_paket`, `pm`.`harga` as `paket_harga`, `k`.`nama_kostum`, `k`.`harga_sewa` as `kostum_harga`, DATEDIFF(p.tanggal_acara, CURDATE()) as days_until_event, CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(p.tanggal_acara, CURDATE()) = 0 THEN "Hari Ini" WHEN DATEDIFF(p.tanggal_acara, CURDATE()) = 1 THEN "Besok" ELSE CONCAT(DATEDIFF(p.tanggal_acara, CURDATE()), " hari lagi") END as time_until_event FROM `pesanan` `p` LEFT JOIN `paket_makeup` `pm` ON `pm`.`id` = `p`.`paket_id` LEFT JOIN `kostum` `k` ON `k`.`id` = `p`.`kostum_id` WHERE `p`.`tanggal_acara` >= '2025-12-25' AND `p`.`tanggal_acara` <= '2026-01-01' AND `p`.`status` IN ('dikonfirmasi','diproses') ORDER BY `p`.`tanggal_acara` ASC, `p`.`created_at` DESC LIMIT 5
